PROPRIETARY STRATEGIC MATERIALS NOTICE

This repository contains proprietary strategic materials for the AHI (Artificial
Hybrid Intelligence) ecosystem, including: planetary-scale vision, architectural
frameworks, governance structures, investment strategies, funding models, licensing
policies, sustainability mechanisms, and long-term strategic planning.

These materials are the exclusive property of Lê Minh Công (Thomas Le) and are
protected by copyright, trade secret, and intellectual property laws.

RELATIONSHIP TO AHI ECOSYSTEM COMPONENTS

This repository serves as the strategic hub for the AHI ecosystem, which comprises:

PROPRIETARY COMPONENTS (Private Repositories):
- AHI-Core: Proprietary cognitive core technologies (memory, reasoning, identity,
           knowledge systems, evolution, regeneration, immortality engines)
- AHI-Investment: Investment structures, funding strategies, ROI policies,
                 licensing models, sustainability mechanisms

PUBLIC COMPONENTS (Open Standards):
- AHI-Framework: Open standards, reference architecture, interoperability
- AHI-Governance: Governance principles, ethics frameworks, consent mechanisms
- AHI-Economy: Knowledge economy, contributor rewards, value distribution
- AHI-Applications: Real-world implementations across sectors

